text: Charles Sturt University is a large Australian university. It has campuses around the world. The university has campuses at Bathurst, Canberra, Albury- Wodonga, Dubbo, Goulburn, Orange, Port Macquarie, Wagga Wagga and Burlington, Ontario (Canada). ==References== Category:Colleges and universities in Australia Category:1989 establishments in Australia
title: Charles Sturt University
